      </p>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0585P0-01287'>
        <a name='S5LV0585P0_19980128_GCR_53'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-clinton-davis' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0585P0_19980128_GCR_53' title='Link to this speech by Mr Clinton Davis' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-clinton-davis" title="Mr Clinton Davis">Lord Clinton-Davis</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
